{"tid":1347054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周國賢-在天之靈","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T09:47:16.000Z","uid":95445,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0afb8b052f350d54e643d0548344caa9fb12d79","tid":1347054,"uid":95445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/giFQnMfHavw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgiFQnMfHavw&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=4740de85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/giFQnMfHavw</a><br />\n作詞: 黃偉文<br />\n作曲: 周國賢<br />\n編曲: Zarahn<br />\n監製: 周國賢 / Goro Wong<br />\n<br />\n不要走 不要走<br />\n你別太早走<br />\n恨還在 病還在<br />\n未曾學會救<br />\n重看你筆記 研究你講義<br />\n和昨日最盛世的地球<br />\n<br />\n不要走 不要走<br />\n應有還未有<br />\n樂園夢 未圓夢<br />\n後人記得 不過沒再追究<br />\n太荒謬<br />\n明知再追幾年 也不夠<br />\n<br />\n遺下美好 當天你讓我去管理<br />\n若果做的 是齣爛戲<br />\n來世沒顏面 見到你<br />\n抬望眾星 在天上看守的百代精靈 <br />\n低頭 我嘆著氣<br />\n<br />\n知了恥 識了書<br />\n被循循善誘<br />\n但求在 學成後<br />\n未來變得比昨日更優秀<br />\n你走後<br />\n崛起那些竟是 禽和獸<br />\n<br />\n遺下美好 今天我代你去管理<br />\n若果做的 是齣爛戲<br />\n來世沒顏面 見到你<br />\n抬望滿山 墓碑亦生輝的 偉大先驅<br />\n後繼著你的福氣 恨我沒有更爭氣<br />\n自上幼稚園 推銷那醜陋<br />\n孩子不聽 要批鬥 <br />\n人間的新審美 你明了沒有<br />\n<br />\n路過意外 亂拍一會 才去救 餵飽手機渴求<br />\n鍵盤愛刻薄 誰要理由 隨手打兩篇毒咒<br />\n<br />\n聽講所有撕裂 搞show可以補救<br />\n豪宅必須供應 農田還剩五六畝 <br />\n<br />\n飯要開 無謂說真話 回家post個 「嬲嬲」足夠<br />\n我是時候自戴手扣<br />\n<br />\n豐功偉業 代你管理<br />\n幸福日子 若果爛尾<br />\n難怪讓泉下你生氣<br />\n<br />\n想給我後世去憶記<br />\n但死後名字 大抵會被他唾棄"},{"pid":"fc51093593c49ef5c8e0130ff6be3e371c38923c","tid":1347054,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"［無政府狀態］元朗恐怖襲擊將成民間自治催産士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa84d315be87818d8c978c99102e8e0a6c154548","tid":1347054,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"好歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48343c972fe7cbb3b5a3585ef6e7e03949baf429","tid":1347054,"uid":36742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"今生不回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63a1516c219c82c6ad784122f72c352fe1453f1","tid":1347054,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"呢d po遲下先啦<br />\n推返d現場元朗上環po上去"},{"pid":"ce42f541d61d8866b6e3f83dc1b0af874d2eb842","tid":1347054,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n<br />\n再聽，哭了"},{"pid":"3d6eaa151dffd3bf783b3426076163593335af34","tid":1347054,"uid":95445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce42f541d61d8866b6e3f83dc1b0af874d2eb842","tid":1347054,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n<br />\n再聽，哭了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"唔好令在天上看守的他們失望<br />\n我哋無論幾累 幾灰都唔好放棄<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"b90c7f42983c66f0324a768f27db7741b4cfeff1","tid":1347054,"uid":256393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}